ActCanada Student Financial Assistance Act
Canada Student Loans Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Canada Student Financial Assistance Regulations and the Canada Student Loans Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADA STUDENT FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE REGULATIONS and the CANADA STUDENT LOANS REGULATIONS in order to complement provincial and territorial initiatives that encourage family physicians, nurses and nurse practitioners to work in under-served rural and remote communities by offering a financial incentive.
